casebody.data:
No. 11-5705 (11A165). Jerry Terrell Jackson, Petitioner v. Loretta K. Kelly, Warden. 564 U.S. 1061, 132 S. Ct. 64,

180 L. Ed. 2d 932,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 5151. August 18, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to The Chief Justice, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.

Justice Ginsburg and Justice Sotomayor would grant the application for stay of execution.

Same case below, 650 F.3d 477.
